# SEO And Metadata

## Per route

- Export `metadata` (or `generateMetadata` when dynamic) with unique `title` and `description`.
- Blog and shareable landings: include `openGraph` (title, description, images when available).
- One clear `h1` per page view (via `PageHero` or section hero).

## Site map

- Base URL: `getSiteUrl()` in `src/lib/site-url.ts` (`NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL` override) — used by `src/app/sitemap.ts`.
- Add static routes when introducing new top-level pages.
- Blog slugs: use `getAllSlugs()` from `@/lib/blog` — do not hardcode slug lists in sitemap.

## Checklist

See `docs/engineering/seo-checklist.md` for robots.txt, JSON-LD, and `metadataBase` follow-ups.

## Avoid

- Duplicate default titles across routes.
- Orphan routes (live URL not in sitemap without intentional `noindex`).
